{
  "texts": [
    "This adaptation not only enhances the properties of concrete but also addresses significant environmental issues associated with cement production.",
    "For instance, producing one ton of cement generates approximately 800 kg of CO 2 emissions, contributing substantially to environmental pollution.",
    "Additionally, the energy consumption for cement production, estimated at 4 GJ per 1.6 tons of natural materials, further intensifies this environmental impact [2].",
    "To reduce the environmental impact of cement production, various SCMs are incorporated into concrete mixes.",
    "These materials are often categorized based on their origins."
  ]
}